---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Tienda — Metalico" description="Explora nuestros productos manufacturados">
  <header class="flex items-center justify-between px-[5%] py-4">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
      </svg>
      Volver al inicio
    </a>
    <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Tienda Metalico</h1>
    <div class="w-20"></div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16">
    <div id="collection-component-1783452024416"></div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Métodos de pago</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
            Tarjetas de débito / crédito (Visa, MasterCard)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
            Transferencia bancaria / SPEI
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
            PayPal
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
            Pago en tienda (previo acuerdo)
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">* Los métodos disponibles se confirmarán al finalizar la compra.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Políticas de compra</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
            Los precios pueden variar sin previo aviso.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
            Las compras se procesan a través de Shopify, plataforma segura.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
            Facturación: envía tu solicitud a contacto@metalico.mx.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Envíos</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
            Envío a toda la República Mexicana.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
            Tiempo estimado de entrega: 5–10 días hábiles.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
            El costo de envío se calcula al momento del pago.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full inline-block mt-1.5 shrink-0"></span>
            Recogida en taller disponible (previa cita).
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Contacto</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <span class="block text-gray-400 text-xs">Correo</span>
            <a href="mailto:contacto@metalico.mx" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">contacto@metalico.mx</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="block text-gray-400 text-xs">Teléfono</span>
            <a href="tel:+525581082193" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">55 8108 2193</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="block text-gray-400 text-xs">WhatsApp</span>
            <a href="https://wa.me/525581082193" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">55 8108 2193</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a href="/privacidad" class="text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-white underline transition-colors">Política de privacidad</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-800">
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-600 py-4">
        &copy; 2026 Metalico. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
/*<![CDATA[*/
